      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some wear and minor staining consistent with regular use. Mechanically, the car has been well-maintained and runs reliably, making it a solid choice for anyone needing a functional vehicle without the price tag of a newer model. It\u2019s an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
