    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and meticulous upkeep. The exterior maintains a high-gloss finish, accented by clean alloy wheels and clear lens housing, with only the slightest signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows minimal wear, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the crisp audio system\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at every recommended interval. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, ensuring it is road-trip ready. If you are looking for a dependable, well-cared-for vehicle that looks as good as it drives, this is the one.",
